{"tid":1317676,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"入咗學堂好似入咗教？","createTime":"2019-07-14T20:28:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-15T02:30:30.000Z","uid":181989,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"40ef6d38adfcafc0e015f456d4a4288894f49496","tid":1317676,"uid":181989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T20:28:20.000Z","msg":"大家發唔發覺？<br />\n身邊有啲人做咗警察之後<br />\n性格同諗嘢都同一般人唔同左<br />\n<br />\n有一個小學同學同佢阿哥都係做警察<br />\n2014年雨傘 都係譴責示威者<br />\n有個男網友做水警 爸爸做警察<br />\n又係覺得示威者搞事<br />\n<br />\n你話一班毅進仔讀書差 <br />\n冇獨立思考能力<br />\n佢哋俾人洗腦都合情理<br />\n但係都有好多人係讀完大學<br />\n甚至喺海外回流返香港<br />\n但入咗學堂就好似信咗教咁<br />\n無論其他人講乜嘢佢哋都聽唔入耳<br />\n<br />\n只係忠誠於警隊內部嘅所謂團結<br />\n就正如朱凱廸所講<br />\n為咗保護自己嘅隊友 完全罔顧法紀<br />\n真係好似一班俾人洗咗腦嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GyR4uYZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGyR4uYZ.png&h=73b23d69&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e1a57442fa82cef036545af86959e8774fd7bd7f","tid":1317676,"uid":123115,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T20:30:14.000Z","msg":"係 特別係身邊做左PI 果堆 <br />\n成個人唔同哂 十足康寶萊nuskin咁 <br />\n勁正面 覺得自己將軍再世咁"},{"pid":"ee98760ead6f0351710847ff294b6616d1798cad","tid":1317676,"uid":29675,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T22:52:22.000Z","msg":"警權同錢會令人腐化"},{"pid":"df5bd1c25e004ab8f2b9490289a88808b1bfa2d6","tid":1317676,"uid":181989,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T02:26:07.000Z","msg":"好恐怖<br />\n點解會咁<br />\n有啲巴打話係為錢<br />\n但我覺得唔止因爲錢<br />\n對佢來講好這種精神支持"},{"pid":"a6161234a779ee1b2ee2ace13d839adf33f98bdd","tid":1317676,"uid":24875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T02:27:43.000Z","msg":"我估佢地已經無左個人意志<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc23919d6bef9fcb7e662233a897b61ed205cbee","tid":1317676,"uid":256514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T02: